00:40:06.319 --> 00:40:09.159  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:34.76%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Nothing to do</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1227
00:40:06.319 --> 00:40:09.159  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but fire it up.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1228
00:40:48.746 --> 00:40:50.666  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>What's all this?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1229
00:40:50.666 --> 00:40:52.106  position:57.62%,start  align:start size:32.86%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You finished</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1230
00:40:50.666 --> 00:40:52.106  position:57.62%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>your work.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1231
00:40:52.106 --> 00:40:54.504  position:51.90%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Now I have</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1232
00:40:52.106 --> 00:40:54.504  position:51.90%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to finish mine.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1233
00:40:54.504 --> 00:40:56.464  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But you don't want to.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1234
00:40:56.464 --> 00:40:58.584  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:67.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I could use a friend on Bajor.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1235
00:40:58.584 --> 00:41:00.303  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'd like it to be you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1236
00:41:00.303 --> 00:41:06.462  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>As long as that cottage</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1237
00:41:00.303 --> 00:41:06.462  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>is standing, I stay here.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1238
00:41:09.301 --> 00:41:11.060  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>What the hell are you doing?!</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1239
00:41:11.060 --> 00:41:13.180  position:48.10%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Saving your life.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1240
00:41:54.647 --> 00:41:57.646  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>So you chose your uniform</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1241
00:41:54.647 --> 00:41:57.646  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>over me after all.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1242
00:41:57.646 --> 00:41:59.006  position:50.00%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That's not true.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1243
00:41:59.006 --> 00:42:01.245  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:25.24%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>The time</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1244
00:41:59.006 --> 00:42:01.245  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I've spent here with you</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1245
00:42:01.245 --> 00:42:03.844  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>has meant so much to me,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1246
00:42:01.245 --> 00:42:03.844  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but it's over.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1247
00:42:03.844 --> 00:42:06.724  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>It's time we went on</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1248
00:42:03.844 --> 00:42:06.724  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>with our lives--</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1249
00:42:06.724 --> 00:42:08.843  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>mine and yours.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1250
00:42:08.843 --> 00:42:11.883  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You say you're my friend.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1251
00:42:11.883 --> 00:42:13.482  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:27.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Prove it.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1252
00:42:13.482 --> 00:42:16.000  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Use that weapon on me.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1253
00:42:18.720 --> 00:42:21.799  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:25.24%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I can't.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1254
00:42:21.799 --> 00:42:24.704  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:59.52%  line:84.62% 
