1255
00:42:24.704 --> 00:42:25.638  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No, you won't.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1256
00:42:25.638 --> 00:42:27.436  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I won't let you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1257
00:42:37.475 --> 00:42:39.674  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Two to beam up.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

